name: arthur-syntax
description: Atom syntax theme based on the Arthur terminal theme
readme:
## Atom Syntax

This Atom theme is identical to the [One Dark](https://atom.io/themes/one-dark-syntax) theme, except that the colors have been replaced with colors found in Arthur terminal theme.

### Install

```
apm install arthur-syntax
```

Or go to __Settings > Install__ and search for `arthur-syntax`.

Then after installing, select "Arthur" from the __Settings > Themes > Syntax Themes__ drop-down menu.
